title: Tangled Hickory Wine Bar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Organic, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Restaurant located downtown offers bistro-style dishes. Has vegetarian options that can be made vegan upon request. Offers large variety of local wines. Uses ingredients from local farmers, bakers and other food producers. Has a retail portion that sells local wines, chocolates and much more. Cozy seating, inviting atmosphere.
